  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of this project is to determine whether prompting the recipient of a health reminder
      mailing to scratch off targeted area.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will randomly assign individuals with different scratch off messages to 3
      groups. The investigators are interested in whether the scratch off message will result in an
      increase in compliance with the recommended health behavior.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
